As a user, I want to be able to sign up so that I can sign in.
As a user, I want to be able to sign in so that I can look up donate location/center, view the inventory.
As a admin, I want to be able to sign up so that I can sign in.
As a admin, I want to be able to sign in so that I can add/remove users, locations, lock/unlock users accounts.
As a admin, I want to be able to change a user status and give user more/less privilege.
As a location employee, I want to be able to sign up so that I can sign in.
As a location employee, I want to be able to sign in so that I can change data.
As a location employee, I want to be able to change data so that I can update info.
As a manager, I want to be able to sign up so that I can sign in.
As a manager, I want to be able to sign in so that I can view and edit all info at all locations.
